OL,3,CJohn Lewis releases early hint of
OL,4,C'through the decades' Christmas ad
OL,6,FWith just under 100 days until
OL,7,FChristmas, John Lewis has released an
OL,8,Fearly hint of its festive advert with
OL,9,Fa new campaign centred on its 'Never
OL,10,FKnowingly Undersold' pledge - its
OL,11,Fpromise to price-match other leading
OL,12,Fretailers.
OL,14,FThe TV ad is the first in a three-part
OL,15,Fcampaign for the all-important retail
OL,16,F'golden quarter', which will culminate
OL,17,Fwith the department store's highly
OL,18,Fanticipated Christmas spot.
