OL,4,C'through the decades' Christmas ad
OL,6,F"We check and match our prices against
OL,7,F25 leading retailers - on the high
OL,8,Fstreet and online too - so you can be
OL,9,Fconfident you're always paying a
OL,10,Fcompetitive price," the John Lewis
OL,11,Fwebsite says.
OL,13,F"If you find the same item for a lower
OL,14,Fprice at one of our listed retailers
OL,15,Fwithin 7 days of buying from us, we'll
OL,16,Frefund the difference."
