OL,3,CJohn Lewis releases early hint of
OL,4,C'through the decades' Christmas ad
OL,6,FJohn Lewis customer director Charlotte
OL,7,FLock said: "We've looked to our
OL,8,Fheritage to inform our refreshed value
OL,9,Fpromise to customers, making it
OL,10,Frelevant for today by matching not
OL,11,Fonly high street retailers but also
OL,12,Fonline competitors - and we are
OL,13,Fbacking it with the biggest marketing
OL,14,Fcampaign in our history.
OL,16,F"We have drawn on our archives and are
OL,17,Fliterally depicting a window on
OL,18,FBritain, showing the changing trends
OL,19,Fand events over the past century," she
OL,20,Fadded.
